Name: Speed Dates Part I
About the game: Important note, language packs will come with the update. SPEED DATES: PART I Our main character Murat attends the Speed Date event and has only a few minutes to get to know the women and make him love himself. Try to impress the girls in this adventure where you can experience today's male-female relationships in the most realistic way. FEATURES • A romantic-comedy FMV game filmed with 19 real actors in 4K. • 54 different paths and 36 different endings. • Over 500 scenes. • High replayability with an estimated 8 hours of gameplay.
